{"tid":1785150,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"呢幾日五毛任務係：吹風瓦解黃色經濟圈","createTime":"2019-12-16T07:24:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-16T12:58:15.000Z","uid":280192,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"a46e881772dced6ace8e35395cf6753344e68730","tid":1785150,"uid":280192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T07:24:11.000Z","msg":"黃色經濟圈力量逐漸形成，對家為左壓制，不斷吹緊：<br />\n<br />\n1. 排斥遲表態的商家入黃圈。<br />\n2. 中立的要打為藍。<br />\n3. 藍割藍，打為扮黃。<br />\n<br />\n咁會整到黃圈越來越細，打擊面太大亦會分薄力量。但我地初心係要越搞越大、針對暴政，大家小心呢類風。"},{"pid":"634a40800f038119804a107df12b8813bee654a1","tid":1785150,"uid":202524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T07:24:57.000Z","msg":"唔好意思 借個位黎<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">德國戰線要人</span></span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">目標：5萬人聯署</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n冇時間啦25號截止，極度要人幫手!<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1782422\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1782422</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"2e0704786796ca9485c5ea79fba11d44404df30d","tid":1785150,"uid":307619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T07:25:08.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">聽晚7點愛丁堡見</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">哀悼香港人道災難</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PY03AQa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPY03AQa.jpg&h=511bc04b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8e3b24833bec1cbad8229a365dae8ec50521cab8","tid":1785150,"uid":196918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T07:32:45.000Z","msg":"推 正視聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig